<para>Interrupt source to attach the callback to. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>callback</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Function to be called when the interrupt occurs. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>context</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
